com.google.closure.plugin.plan

Class JoinNodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.closure.plugin.plan.JoinNodes

  • public final class JoinNodes
extends Object
    Pub/sub system based on input and output source file extensions to link sub-graphs together without tight coupling.

    A producer of *.foo that knows of nothing that should follow it may depend on the AfterFoo join node.

    Consumers of *.foo generated files can register themselves as followers of AfterFoo.
